docs.abstract: “Colin Kaepernick: Change the Game,” an illustrated book, follows a young athlete choosing between baseball, which seems like a sure path, and football, where he feels he can be himself.
docs.snippet: “Colin Kaepernick: Change the Game,” an illustrated book, follows a young athlete choosing between baseball, which seems like a sure path, and football, where he feels he can be himself.
docs.lead_paragraph: As Colin Kaepernick approached the end of high school, he had a decision to make: He could pursue baseball, for which he was already being scouted, or he could try to play football, a sport where he felt he could embrace his community and his identity.

headline.main: Colin Kaepernick to Publish a Young Adult Memoir
